# Mobile Feature Pattern

**Aplicar automáticamente**: FRONTEND_STANDARDS.md y DESIGN_SYSTEM.md. No requiere que el usuario lo mencione.

## Stack
- Expo Router (file-based): `app/` directory
- NativeWind (Tailwind) for styles
- Zustand for local state, React Query for server state
- Hooks: useWorkouts, useExercises, useSocial, etc. in `src/hooks/`

## New screen flow
1. Add route in `app/{path}.tsx` or `app/{folder}/`
2. Use existing hooks if API exists
3. UI: Card, Button, Input, Avatar, Badge from `src/components/ui/`
4. Auth: wrap with auth check or use (tabs) layout

## API integration
- Add/use client in `src/services/api/`
- Create hook in `src/hooks/use{Feature}.ts` with React Query
- Handle loading, error states

## Text & Fonts
- Use `Text` from `@/components/ui/Text` (not `react-native` Text) for correct Spanish characters (á, é, í, ó, ú).
- Fonts: `font-heading` (Poppins), `font-body` (Inter), `font-label` (Montserrat).

## Brand (source: `mobile/tailwind.config.js`)
- Primary: `#9D12DE` (purple). Use `bg-primary`, `text-primary`.
- Accent: `#FFEA00` (yellow). Use `bg-highlight`, `text-highlight`.
- Background/Surface: `#262626`. Use `bg-background`, `bg-surface`.
- Text: `#E3E3E3`. Use `text-text`.
- Fonts: `font-heading` (Poppins), `font-body` (Inter), `font-label` (Montserrat).
- Do not hardcode hex colors. Use Tailwind tokens and DESIGN_SYSTEM.md.
